{"tid":2063873,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國製OLED螢幕質量差劣，連奶共Apple都表示冇法啃得落","createTime":"2020-06-14T10:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T05:51:36.000Z","uid":48040,"like":259,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1f3f14262b42ae3a73b453ce8d29db25ea3672","tid":2063873,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T10:58:53.000Z","msg":"Apple一直好想將iPhone螢幕訂單比中國廠商，以符合其<del>奶共</del>企業理念。但可惜中國廠家「京東方」唔爭氣，最新消息指京東方的螢幕質量太差劣，無法達到iPhone12的要求。<br />\n<br />\n6月13日，據外媒報導，供應鏈報告顯示，OLED 供應商京東方（BOE）未能通過蘋果公司 iPhone 12 的首輪質量檢查。儘管目前尚不清楚 iPhone 12 何時開始大規模生產，但該設備的零部件需要儘快交付。根據最新的供應鏈報告，京東方（BOE）正在努力解決質量問題，但未能通過首輪屏幕測試。<br />\n<br />\nDdaily 在周五的一份報告中表示，除沒有達到蘋果要求外，京東方也沒有達到三星的要求。報告稱，京東方將再次嘗試，並向兩家公司提交一批新產品。報導指出，三星仍然是蘋果 OLED 屏幕的主要供應商。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20200614/35463088.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20200614%2F35463088.html&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJkn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=f87b8db0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20200614/35463088.html</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wlXPiafyjLc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwlXPiafyjLc&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJkn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=435855da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wlXPiafyjLc</a>"},{"pid":"7216abd7d64572bf5a5b0460b4d2be0c39b4f792","tid":2063873,"uid":38904,"like":152,"dislike":2,"score":150,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T11:00:15.000Z","msg":"中國做嘅嘢<br />\n絕對係<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">垃圾</span></span>品質保證<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d78297ff4bdd0c415241b12acc60453862b611","tid":2063873,"uid":48040,"like":89,"dislike":3,"score":86,"quote":{"pid":"7216abd7d64572bf5a5b0460b4d2be0c39b4f792","tid":2063873,"uid":38904,"like":152,"dislike":2,"score":150,"citedBy":5